*INSTRUCTIONS*

0. make sure you have "python" and "venv" installed on your maschine

1. create local environment running "python -m venv env"

2. activate it using ". ./env/Scripts/activate" (might differ for Unix system)

3. install dependencies listed in "requirements.txt" using command "pip install -r requirements.txt"

4. you can verify installation using "pip list"

5. run the project using "uvicorn main:app --reload"

*TIPS*
# The command uvicorn main:app refers to:
    main: the file main.py (the Python "module").
    app: the object created inside of main.py with the line app = FastAPI().
    --reload: make the server restart after code changes. Only do this for development.

# you can visit http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs to see swagger API structure

